section.div: Deeper Seeker is an simpler OSS version of OpenAI's latest Deep Research feature in ChatGPT.It is an agentic research tool to reason , create multi step tasks , synthesize data from multiple online resources and create neat reports
Agent Laboratory is an end-to-end autonomous research workflow meant to assist you as the human researcher toward implementing your research ideas
